--- Total Simplex = (Score Variance, c3) ---
total_sigma = sum(s_i^2) - n(n-1)/2 = n*Var(scores) + n*(n-1)^2/4 - n(n-1)/2
  where Var = sum(s_i - mean)^2 / n, mean = (n-1)/2
total_lambda = 3 * c3
total_delta = n(n-1)(n-2)/2 + n(n-1)/2 - sum(s^2) - 3*c3

So the 'total simplex position' is completely determined by (score_variance, c3)!
The INDIVIDUAL pair positions carry additional structure beyond these totals.


